value.0: Leave my sight you evil creature. Leave my sight and never return!
There's no replacement for family but you look like a friendly face...
<StartCheck>[Failure]</Start> W-what? You... you would rob me in the street in full view of anyone walking by? Are you insane? What about guards? What about watchmen?
<StartCheck>[Success]</Start> But... no, please! I... I just want to get through all of this alive! Here... take it! Take all the gold I have! Take it and... and get out of my sight... just go...
And if you want a sucker to absorb damage for ya, visit the Trade of Blades mercenary enclave in the City Core.
Do you want to hear about the Beggar's Nest? The Docks? The Blacklake? The prison? The City Core? Take your pick - I have a lifetime, however short.
You really don't know the city if you have to ask. Everybody knows about Neverwinter's famous prison.
<StartCheck>[Intimidate]</Start> To find out if you have gold! Hand it over, now!
<StartCheck>[Bluff]</Start> I have the cure! Give me all your gold and you can have it!

LinkComment.value: You evil piece of garbage... you took all I had left. Get out of my sight... get out!!
